<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Application Approved - 12done.com</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; border-bottom: 2px solid #4F46E5; }
    .logo { font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #4F46E5; }
    .content { padding: 30px 0; }
    .status-badge { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .congratulations { font-size: 28px; color: #10B981; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .info-box { background: #ECFDF5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #D1FAE5; }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .info-label { color: #065F46; }
    .info-value { color: #047857; font-weight: 500; }
    .button { display: inline-block; background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; margin: 20px 0; }
    .next-steps { background: #F3F4F6; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .next-steps h3 { margin-top: 0; color: #374151; }
    .next-steps ol { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    .next-steps li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 20px 0; color: #666; font-size: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin-top: 30px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <div class="logo">12done.com</div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="status-badge">Approved</div>

    <h1 class="congratulations">Congratulations!</h1>

    <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>

    <p>Great news! Your rental application for "{{propertyTitle}}" has been <strong>approved</strong> by the property owner.</p>

    <div class="info-box">
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Application Details</h3>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Property</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{propertyTitle}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Owner</span>
        <span class="info-value">{{ownerName}}</span>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <span class="info-label">Status</span>
        <span class="info-value" style="color: #10B981;">Approved</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="next-steps">
      <h3>Next Steps</h3>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Review the lease terms</strong> - The owner will prepare the lease agreement</li>
        <li><strong>Sign the lease</strong> - You'll receive the lease for e-signature</li>
        <li><strong>Pay the deposit</strong> - Complete the security deposit payment</li>
        <li><strong>Move in!</strong> - Coordinate move-in details with the owner</li>
      </ol>
    </div>

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">View Application Details</a>
    </p>

    <p>The property owner may reach out to you soon to discuss the next steps. You can also message them directly through our platform.</p>

    <p>Welcome to your new home!</p>

    <p>Best regards,<br>The 12done.com Team</p>
  </div>

  <div class="footer">
    <p>&copy; {{year}} 12done.com. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>This is a transactional email regarding your rental application on 12done.com.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
